{"type": "article", "id": 25140, "title": "可旋转灯源的手提灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-08T07:02:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 60, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702144057rxM3Z4ymWV2PHAo5.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这盏手提灯的外形像一个水壶，它有一个球形的可转动的 LED 光源。光源下面使用了一种塑料低密度聚乙烯（LDPE），当光源转动向下时，可通过塑料本身散发出柔和的光线，就像一盏小夜灯。这盏灯是通过 USB 接口充电，当电充满后，可以以最高亮度持续 10 个小时。售价 98 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.weltevreeshop.nl/guidelight.html\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144055hxDLGgVv430Que8f.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144055NjChu6kTcOXnqwvD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144055YKmxRAaIwTJc3oL1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021440567l1PZAK3XSLTMFVg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021440571kEprvbnlVcYO9y8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}